          "en": "Microsoft researchers, in collaboration with Princeton University and Universitat Politècnica de València, introduced ADeLe to predict and explain AI performance across various tasks.",
          "zh": "微软研究院研究人员与普林斯顿大学及瓦伦西亚理工大学合作，推出了ADeLe框架，旨在预测并解释AI在不同任务中的表现。"
        },
        "key_takeaways": {
          "en": [
            "Current AI benchmarks show LLM performance on specific tasks without explaining underlying capabilities.",
            "ADeLe is a new framework designed to predict and explain AI performance.",
            "The framework was developed by Microsoft researchers in collaboration with Princeton University and Universitat Politècnica de València."
          ],
          "zh": [
            "当前AI基准测试报告大型语言模型（LLM）在特定任务上的表现，但未能深入揭示其潜在能力。",
            "ADeLe是一个旨在预测和解释AI性能的新框架。",
            "该框架由微软研究人员与普林斯顿大学和瓦伦西亚理工大学合作开发。"
          ]
        },
        "impact": {
          "en": "This development aims to provide deeper insights into AI model behavior beyond simple performance metrics. By explaining failures and predicting outcomes, ADeLe could enhance the reliability and development of AI systems.",
          "zh": "这一进展旨在提供超越简单性能指标的AI模型行为的更深层洞察。通过解释故障和预测结果，ADeLe有望提升AI系统的可靠性和开发效率。"
        },
        "source": "Microsoft Research",
        "link": "https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/adele-predicting-and-explaining-ai-performance-across-tasks/"
